data.description: Under Contract! Bright, cheery, and beautifully maintained solid brick ranch with finished basement in a friendly Westmont neighborhood. This home features hardwood floors, updated baths, stainless steel appliances, a newer water heater and refrigerator, a new privacy fence, a Nest thermostat, and a brand new premium garage door (2021) and dishwasher (2021). The lower level adds an extra 1000 sq. ft. of phenomenal space. Relax or entertain in the spacious family room featuring a wet bar, built-in surround sound system, a bonus exercise/office/playroom, and a full bath with heated floors. This home is an inspector's dream: updated plumbing with copper pipes, chimney tuck pointed, high R-value insulation, venting added to attic, new concrete walkway, stairs and stoop reconstruction...the list goes on! You'll love the peaceful, fully fenced back yard with a paver brick patio, garden area, and a shed for extra storage. You just can't beat this location! Less than a mile from vibrant downtown Westmont and the nearby shopping center with a Starbucks, LA Fitness, and Amazon Fresh. Highly rated schools, including Downers Grove North HS and Maercker District schools. A quick walk to the Metra and easy access to interstates. Welcome home.
